      <abstract>
         <para>AutoYaST is a system for unattended mass deployment of <phrase role="productname">SUSE Linux Enterprise Server</phrase> systems. It uses an AutoYaST profile that contains installation and configuration data. The book guides you through the basic steps of auto-installation: preparation, installation, and configuration.</para>
      </abstract>
